ckquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n叫咗你讀好啲physics 架啦"},{"pid":"026a1b46ab10c88c431cb6314183def5da1897f8","tid":461534,"uid":154702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2017/09/19/iphone-x-face-id-truedepth-vcsel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2Fiphone-x-face-id-truedepth-vcsel%2F&d=%2B8t1zD76Akrb5gSLLcVgAtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2ed4f3ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2017/09/19/iphone-x-face-id-truedepth-vcsel/</a><br />\n<br />\n介紹得幾好<br />\n值得一睇"},{"pid":"7c47a9fd1fc8e5459f11b501e83a11ef133e9427","tid":461534,"uid":144924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:46:24.000Z","msg":"咁快就有人沖出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c7cd24e8db9c9bbce2680b549deb9dfdfbc41d","tid":461534,"uid":154702,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你係講緊文中既『<span style=\"color: red;\">飛時測距（ToF：Time of Flight）</span>』<br />\n<br />\n 至於&ldquo;4k Mon 論&rdquo; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n唔會係3D 啦&hellip;你睇到有影像唔代表有實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係錄播黎，源於平面既螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n但鏡就會反射埋實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係源於環境光照落你面容既反射<br />\n<br />\n我係咪認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5325d4da9ec8d60fd954c1d9ec63e2d4891e39","tid":461534,"uid":7622,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"我咁理解<br />\n鏡係直接反射，所以解到鎖<br />\n相片/影片雖然係用有鏡片既機器，最後係折射落一個平面到跟住再顯示出黎，即使視覺上睇落3D/好立體，但始終係一個平面，所以解唔到鎖<br />\n有冇錯？<br />\n<br />\n利申：文科撚"},{"pid":"10aa3375c4f3c1ca1bbd59c83d59ccba8f77c8cd","tid":461534,"uid":144312,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"有讀physic覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94981ef051313451e92e6d4605ffc82d8e76adae","tid":461534,"uid":146924,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有讀physic覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上係有少少柒嘅 但唔好講到好似唔知就等於弱智咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6633a89be4e943d784bf8a014e9b45be6f18643b","tid":461534,"uid":76428,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:21:15.000Z","msg":"反射/折射=3D<br />\n投影屏幕=2D"},{"pid":"1cbf14a2cb6b9335543060a9d09850f1c0093071","tid":461534,"uid":146924,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d610d8eaf8c5d618018df72d097ec07282052ef","tid":461534,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？"},{"pid":"b7949eac6d6e6c8597f0caf967f0d9e15b55c808","tid":461534,"uid":75868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？</blockquote><br />\n比你複製到，咪又係要用個平既mon投影出黎<br />\n一係用本人既3D影像再整個佢既樣既模型出黎"},{"pid":"eb6858ff19d2319fab3ec7760c5be2bdedef11da","tid":461534,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T20:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？</blockquote><br />\n比你複製到，咪又係要用個平既mon投影出黎<br />\n一係用本人既3D影像再整個佢既樣既模型出黎</blockquote><br />\n我讀文科, 亦都唔明原理. <br />\n不過我十幾年前玩相機, 試過對住塊鏡對焦影相. 原來塊鏡係有淺景深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5080386a7d0c711509dfce780f0325a08c70a641","tid":461534,"uid":144312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T20:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有讀physic覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上係有少少柒嘅 但唔好講到好似唔知就等於弱智咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話覺得佢弱智，純粹睇住唔識嘅人，用佢嘅理解去解釋好笑啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354df98de06de5f93f44c27bb9a11f059c8bf89a","tid":461534,"uid":85909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T20:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？</blockquote><br />\n比你複製到，咪又係要用個平既mon投影出黎<br />\n一係用本人既3D影像再整個佢既樣既模型出黎</blockquote><br />\n我讀文科, 亦都唔明原理. <br />\n不過我十幾年前玩相機, 試過對住塊鏡對焦影相. 原來塊鏡係有淺景深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇留意到拍片條友要望鏡頭先解到鎖，<br />\n<br />\n即係就算係鏡反射情況下，都要機主望住鏡入邊嘅iphone x先會解鎖"},{"pid":"e42242dcd3089643433067971fbdd567b4d0521a","tid":461534,"uid":98474,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T20:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/044010_d8be0ccc2d00827aa7cc1923f58ccb4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F044010_d8be0ccc2d00827aa7cc1923f58ccb4d.jpg&h=c0800657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b35060d610eab7547425bfa5e767afa23a25fb32","tid":461534,"uid":146924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T21:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？</blockquote><br />\n我意思唔係話複製鏡像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而係用face ID如果你攞咗我部電話想解鎖，<br />\n原本要將部電話放喺我面前，<br />\n咁嘅情況基本上我係一定會發現<br />\n<br />\n但係而家可以隔住幾塊鏡反射完之後再解鎖，<br />\n咁人哋咪可以似側側地擺幾塊鏡，將我嘅樣3D咁樣反射去解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47919363a6ff27fc542ab4b6d9b5248230192e33","tid":461534,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T21:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？</blockquote><br />\n我意思唔係話複製鏡像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而係用face ID如果你攞咗我部電話想解鎖，<br />\n原本要將部電話放喺我面前，<br />\n咁嘅情況基本上我係一定會發現<br />\n<br />\n但係而家可以隔住幾塊鏡反射完之後再解鎖，<br />\n咁人哋咪可以似側側地擺幾塊鏡，將我嘅樣3D咁樣反射去解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你放幾多塊鏡反射都好<br />\n你都要望住電話個鏡頭對準先解到鎖"},{"pid":"464705bb1913a2f98c838578e1a0eb2cde6b5b56","tid":461534,"uid":154264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T22:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80088fda1a9b3565c3d2f4cfd055caf2359bdf37","tid":461534,"uid":58527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T22:15:43.000Z","msg":"但左右調轉左都認到係咪先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fef3b4b97bc5e977bd139567752b2d12833452e","tid":461534,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T22:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1d3961434e405a00feadd2fa14bb8ab37ecdd31","tid":461534,"uid":47128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T22:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家有冇技術可以複製鏡像？</blockquote><br />\n我意思唔係話複製鏡像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而係用face ID如果你攞咗我部電話想解鎖，<br />\n原本要將部電話放喺我面前，<br />\n咁嘅情況基本上我係一定會發現<br />\n<br />\n但係而家可以隔住幾塊鏡反射完之後再解鎖，<br />\n咁人哋咪可以似側側地擺幾塊鏡，將我嘅樣3D咁樣反射去解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你放幾多塊鏡反射都好<br />\n你都要望住電話個鏡頭對準先解到鎖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有個距離限制<br />\n我估同部電話超過一米就解唔到"},{"pid":"cacf65d007b62