\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb03beca8a15bcc8ed040f303d02ee599663c49a","tid":461534,"uid":9887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲測試其實好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果用鏡反射係可以解到嘅話，咁機主會多咗風險係喺唔知情嘅情況底下俾人解鎖咗部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你比人攞左電話，再喺你隔離對住望住鏡入面既你去解鎖<br />\n如果你咁都唔知不如死左去"},{"pid":"b5ad24dd39b4850f2bf6ae3c69e0b2ef21204026","tid":461534,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n潛咗去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你上水發表偉論啊"},{"pid":"e30ee89ec05f2419ca3feab32c7613a9b98d7419","tid":461534,"uid":55598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你係講緊文中既『<span style=\"color: red;\">飛時測距（ToF：Time of Flight）</span>』<br />\n<br />\n 至於&ldquo;4k Mon 論&rdquo; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n唔會係3D 啦&hellip;你睇到有影像唔代表有實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係錄播黎，源於平面既螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n但鏡就會反射埋實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係源於環境光照落你面容既反射<br />\n<br />\n我係咪認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比起班笑人既傻仔呢啲回覆先高汁"},{"pid":"0ffb152a70acad83a712561f49fa72e553f5e825","tid":461534,"uid":96855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有讀physic覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上係有少少柒嘅 但唔好講到好似唔知就等於弱智咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知冇問題 唔知又要發表偉論嘅唔係弱智係咩？"},{"pid":"3e135efae0e0b81d4448eaa5dcaba6ca48b287b6","tid":461534,"uid":101337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但左右調轉左都認到係咪先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\niOS 好多App都support 上下反轉嚟用架啦, 我諗右左調轉都support係因為預左果啲app會用face ID 認證"},{"pid":"1ba1c3e04bd15c9c79d6ce0962f1102945771911","tid":461534,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"如果個topic係三星嘅話一定正評多個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bbdd272d3454ec2aa8936b0349bd9741a141b2","tid":461534,"uid":134623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e55bbfca2cd0f3292d14efb15058f990bdddd43","tid":461534,"uid":54951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家以為鏡係平面 所以face id會fail<br />\n<br />\n其實係紅外投射儀向鏡發射3萬個紅外測量點<br />\n<br />\n經鏡子反射到事主臉部<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone係<span style=\"color: red;\">用一個紅外攝影機</span>拍攝呢d點<br />\n<br />\n然後係cpu內計算測量點陣之間距離 <br />\n推算出三維臉部模型<br />\nmatch後 將手機解鎖<br />\n<br />\n紅字講明係一個 即係2d<br />\n只有雙眼/雙攝像頭先可以透過視差睇到3d影像<br />\n所以iphone 的3d測量並非用雙紅外攝像頭達成<br />\n係用單粒紅外攝像頭拍攝 然後用cpu計算點距之差去計算出3d臉部模型</blockquote><br />\n呢個係真正答案<br />\n我唔明係因為舊有技術用pulse 時間距離，通常係用ultrasonic唔係光<br />\n光測唔到反射速度因為太快，所以用點距差<br />\n笑人個d純粹明鏡會反射咋下話？"},{"pid":"735abc97184103a42e37512e6c6a1f8780b8aae2","tid":461534