mal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e168c8355c2d21e074e01f69c5da0b103013226","tid":461534,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你係講緊文中既『<span style=\"color: red;\">飛時測距（ToF：Time of Flight）</span>』<br />\n<br />\n 至於&ldquo;4k Mon 論&rdquo; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n唔會係3D 啦&hellip;你睇到有影像唔代表有實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係錄播黎，源於平面既螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n但鏡就會反射埋實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係源於環境光照落你面容既反射<br />\n<br />\n我係咪認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比起班笑人既傻仔呢啲回覆先高汁</blockquote><br />\n如果用有輕微弧度嘅鏡反射電視影像，會唔會呃到個Sensor有景深存在？<br />\n文科撚純鳩諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4c274715102373518dcaadb66efff4b77c5669","tid":461534,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你係講緊文中既『<span style=\"color: red;\">飛時測距（ToF：Time of Flight）</span>』<br />\n<br />\n 至於&ldquo;4k Mon 論&rdquo; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n唔會係3D 啦&hellip;你睇到有影像唔代表有實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係錄播黎，源於平面既螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n但鏡就會反射埋實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係源於環境光照落你面容既反射<br />\n<br />\n我係咪認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比起班笑人既傻仔呢啲回覆先高汁</blockquote><br />\n如果用有輕微弧度嘅鏡反射電視影像，會唔會呃到個Sensor有景深存在？<br />\n文科撚純鳩諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要解鎖應該唔單止係弧度<br />\n係要整個輪廓<br />\n好似樓上有ching提過<br />\nface ID之所以咁op <br />\n係因為佢係 camera + 3d scanner 二合為一"},{"pid":"99d303b72e96121a07618ee0c8a8996bfc86df12","tid":461534,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影機影, 4k mon播 都係源頭3d<br />\n咁我都會以為佢3d既技術係用pulse反射時間去計距離-&gt;真正3d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你係講緊文中既『<span style=\"color: red;\">飛時測距（ToF：Time of Flight）</span>』<br />\n<br />\n 至於&ldquo;4k Mon 論&rdquo; &hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n唔會係3D 啦&hellip;你睇到有影像唔代表有實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係錄播黎，源於平面既螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n但鏡就會反射埋實際景深<br />\n因為你睇到既光(影像)係源於環境光照落你面容既反射<br />\n<br />\n我係咪認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比起班笑人既傻仔呢啲回覆先高汁</blockquote><br />\n如果用有輕微弧度嘅鏡反射電視影像，會唔會呃到個Sensor有景深存在？<br />\n文科撚純鳩諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係要眼耳口鼻嘅正確景深 唔係單單check有冇弧度<br />\n就好似點解近視嘅人睇遠嘢睇唔清<br />\n不過用鏡頭影低就可以係mon睇到"},{"pid":"44c405979983fddb9f7951566629c0411c192a2d","tid":461534,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話３Ｄ面容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾心機讀好physics <br />\n用左鏡反射返黎點會唔係3d面容？<br />\n個源頭咪又係3D .....</blockquote><br />\n你咁講拎勁既攝影